4.Mark tickets as "VIP" if customer name starts with A, E, M, or S
mysql> select *,case
    -> when left(customer_name,1) in ('a','e','m','s') then 'vip'
    -> else 'regular'
    -> end as vip_status
    -> from tickets;
+-----------+---------------+------------+----------+-----------+--------------+---------------+---------------+------------+
